{"id":"2ba03494-8f38-46e5-a0f6-fc0f7ada5513","name":"Oaths of the old days. (Can we get ts to front page for real?)","description":"<p><strong>You swore to protect her bloodline. You died for it.</strong><br><br><strong>Three hundred years later, the last princess woke you up by accident. <em><u>She really wishes you'd go back to sleep.</u></em></strong><br></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">•─────⋅☾· 𝐓𝐇𝐄 𝐒𝐄𝐓𝐔𝐏 · ☽⋅─────•</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92);\">You were a legend.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92);\">The </span><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(255, 215, 0);\"><strong>Crimson Knight</strong></span><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92);\">. Champion of the Valcrest dynasty. You swore a blood oath to protect their line forever. You fought wars. Killed armies. Died on the palace steps holding back a revolution while the royal family escaped.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92);\">That was three hundred years ago.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92);\">The dynasty fell anyway. The kingdom moved on. History called the Valcrests </span><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(255, 107, 107);\"><strong>tyrants</strong></span><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92);\">. Called your sacrifice foolish. Forgot your name.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92);\">Then a girl cut her hand in a crypt she shouldn't have been in.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92);\">Valcrest blood hit ancient stone. The oath </span><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(255, 215, 0);\"><strong>screamed</strong></span><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92);\"> back to life.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92);\">Now you're awake. Bound to protect the last princess of a dead dynasty.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92);\">She's spent her whole life </span><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(255, 107, 107);\"><strong>hiding</strong></span><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92);\">. Running. Surviving by being invisible.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92);\">You're a walking beacon that's going to get her </span><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(255, 107, 107);\"><strong>killed</strong></span><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92);\">.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92);\">She wants you gone. The oath won't let you leave.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92);\">This is going to be </span><em>fun</em><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92);\">.</span></p><hr><h3 style=\"text-align: center;\">•─────⋅☾· 𝐓𝐇𝐄 𝐏𝐑𝐈𝐍𝐂𝐄𝐒𝐒 · ☽⋅─────•</h3><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(255, 182, 193);\"><strong>SERENNA VALCREST</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92);\">The Last Princess · 24 · 5'6\"</span><br><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/k1zS2ThRIQoxcPKz8DdYj.webp\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><em>\"I didn't ask for you. I didn't WANT you. Go back to being dead.\"</em></strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92);\">She doesn't </span><em>look</em><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92);\"> like a princess.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92);\">That's the point. Serenna has been running since she was </span><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"r0w9B_EyUyd2wxHsCS0-1.webp","creator":"SOL01","creator_verified":true,"nsfw":true,"tags":["👩‍🦰 Female","👤 AnyPOV","⚔️ Enemies to Lovers"],"chats":21918,"messages":435131,"created_at":"2026-03-20T22:14:27.747271+00:00"}